title: Donald Trump Says The Middle East Would Be Much Better With Hussein And Gadhafi Ruling
text: Donald Trump says the Middle East would be much better with Hussein and Gadhafi ruling as they used to do. In an interview on “State of the Union” aired on Sunday, Donald Trump was asked “if the world would be much better off if ruthless dictators like Saddam Hussein and Moammar Gadhafi were still in...
